<li>Deely, John. (2000), <i>The Red Book: The Beginning of Postmodern Times or: Charles Sanders Peirce and the Recovery of</i> Signum. <span class="PDFlink"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.helsinki.fi/science/commens/papers/redbook.pdf">Eprint</a></span><span style="font-size:smaller;">&#160;PDF&#160;(578&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kibibyte" title="Kibibyte">KiB</a>)</span>.</li>
