<li>Deely, John. (2001). <i>Four Ages of Understanding</i>. Toronto: University of Toronto Press.</li>
<li>Deely, John. (2003), "On the Word Semiotics, Formation and Origins", <i>Semiotica</i> 146.1/4, 1–50.</li>
