<li>Deely, John. (2004), "'<span lang="grc" xml:lang="grc">Σημειον</span>' to 'Sign' by Way of 'Signum': On the Interplay of Translation and Interpretation in the Establishment of Semiotics", <i>Semiotica</i> 148–1/4, 187–227.</li>
<li>Deely, John. (2006), "On 'Semiotics' as Naming the Doctrine of Signs", <i>Semiotica</i> 158.1/4 (2006), 1–33.</li>
